Class THashMap<K,V>

    MethodMap

    public class THashMap<K,V>
extends TObjectHash<K>
implements gnu.trove.map.TMap<K,V>, Externalizable
    An implementation of the Map interface which uses an open addressed hash table to store its contents.

    Created: Sun Nov 4 08:52:45 2001

    Version:
    $Id: THashMap.java,v 1.1.2.8 2010/03/02 04:09:50 robeden Exp $
    Author:
    Eric D. Friedman, Rob Eden, Jeff Randall
